file: CoreCommandKind.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Domain\\Command\\CoreCommandKind"
type: final class
summary: Defines the set of core command types recognized by the agent core system. This final class provides a static utility to validate whether a given command kind string belongs to the core domain. It serves as a strict type guard for command routing and processing.
